    "body": "## Complete V2.0 Release\n\nThis is a comprehensive update with three major feature modules.\n\n---\n\n### Module 1: Authentic Bazi Calculation Engine\n**Traditional Chinese Four Pillars (四柱八字) with accurate methods:**\n\n- **Year Pillar (年柱)**: Sexagenary Cycle with 立春 (Li Chun) boundary adjustment\n- **Month Pillar (月柱)**: 五虎遁 (Five Tigers) formula with 24 Solar Terms  \n- **Day Pillar (日柱)**: Sexagenary Cycle from 1900 baseline (甲戌)\n- **Hour Pillar (时柱)**: 五鼠遁 (Five Rats) formula with 2-hour periods\n- **Hidden Stems (藏干)**: Primary/Secondary/Tertiary extraction\n- **Da Yun (大运)**: Complete luck pillar calculation with direction determination\n- **Element Scoring**: Comprehensive algorithm with Ten God framework\n\n---\n\n### Module 2: Mental Models Framework (NEW)\n**15 element-based mental models from Chinese philosophy:**\n\n**Wood**: Growth Mindset, Root Before Branch, Flexible Persistence  \n**Fire**: Controlled Burn, Illumination Strategy, Transformational Catalyst  \n**Earth**: Container Principle, Seasonal Timing, Nourishing Support  \n**Metal**: Precise Division, Structural Integrity, Refinement Process  \n**Water**: Adaptive Flow, Penetrating Insight, Depth Accumulation\n\n**5 Decision Frameworks:**\n1. Five Element Decision Matrix (五行决)\n2. Seasonal Timing (待时而动)\n3. Ten God Interaction (十神应用)\n4. Root and Branch Analysis (本末先后)\n5. Branch Interaction (地支运筹)\n\n---\n\n### Module 3: ERC-8004 KOL Insights (NEW) - Standalone\n**Track thought leaders in the agent economy:**\n\n| Handle | Name | Focus | Priority |\n|--------|------|-------|----------|\n| @MarcoMetaMask | Marco De Rossi | Production AI, Survival Tech | High |\n| @dcrapis | Davide Crapis | Standards, Protocol Design | Critical |\n| @erc_8004 | ERC-8004 | Technical specification | Critical |\n| @MichaelRKantor | Michael Kantor | Education, Explanations | Medium |\n\n**Mental Models Extracted:**\n- Production Reality Check (@MarcoMetaMask)\n- Standards Create Societies (@dcrapis)\n- Three Registries Architecture (@dcrapis)\n- Agent as Economic Actor (@dcrapis)\n- Protocol-First Design (@erc_8004)\n- Pluggable Trust Models (@erc_8004)\n- Reputation as Hiring Signal (@MichaelRKantor)\n\n**Features:**\n- Searchable by keyword/domain\n- Source attribution with links\n- Application guidelines\n- Export to mental model format\n\n*Standalone module - no link to Bazi*\n\n---\n\n### API Endpoints\n\n```\n/api/mental-models     - Elemental mental models\n```\n\n**Access via code:**\n```typescript\nimport { \n    MarcoDeRossi, DavideCrapis, MichaelKantor, ERC8004Org,\n    searchKOLInsights, convertKOLToMentalModels \n} from \"@/lib/mental_models\";\n```\n\n---\n\n### Files Changed\n- lib/bazi/bazi_core.ts ~850 lines (complete rewrite)\n- lib/cycles/dayun.ts ~350 lines (new)\n- lib/mental_models/*.ts ~1,600 lines (new module)\n- lib/interpretation/*.ts (enhanced)\n\n**Total: ~3,000+ lines**\n\n---\n\n*Veritas Vult*\n<!-- devin-review-badge-begin -->\n\n---\n\n<a href=\"https://app.devin.ai/review/0x-wzw/bazi_daily_decision_tree/pull/28\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://static.devin.ai/assets/gh-open-in-devin-review-dark.svg?v=1\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.devin.ai/assets/gh-open-in-devin-review-light.svg?v=1\" alt=\"Open with Devin\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<!-- devin-review-badge-end -->\n",
